A Flask + SQLite admin dashboard, fully runnable on port 5086.

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `app.py` | App factory, routes, security headers, error handlers, CLI (`init-db`, `create-admin`) |
| `config.py` | Env-driven config; refuses to start without `SECRET_KEY` |
