One note for local HTTP testing: keep `SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE=false` in `.env` (already set in the example) ‚Äî otherwise the browser won't send the session cookie over plain HTTP and login will appear to fail. Set it back to `true` behind HTTPS in production. Full details are in `README.md`.
